        "Lockdowns to Contain COVID-19 Increase Risk and Severity of Mosquito-Borne Disease Outbreaks",
        'The future course of the COVID-19 pandemic is still unclear at this time; while we may hope that it goes away very quickly, it may well sustain in some form for a long while to come, including by returning in a "second wave", or by becoming a seasonal disease.',
