//         "As part of this retrospective, service evaluation, the first 500 consecutive COVID-19 postive admissions to ESTH were evaluated. All patients included in this service evaluation were swabbed, either as in-patients or when they presented to the emergency department with coronavirus like symptoms. Each swab sample was recorded onto a patient electronic record system with a date and time stamp. If the sample was detected as postive, the COVID-19 postive result was recorded with a date and time stamp.",
