//         "The data was extracted from two patient electronic record systems: Clinical Manager (Clinical Manager Version 2.0, vMware Horizon Client. iSOFT) and Ward Watcher software (Critical Care Audit Ltd).",
//         "Data was tabulated using Microsoft Excel (Microsoft, Redmond, WA). Data analysis was undertaken on Microsoft Excel (Microsoft, Redmond, WA) and SPSS Version 23 (IBM, SPSS Statistics). Statistical analysis was undertaken using odd ratios, risk ratios and the Fisher's exact test. The level of significance was set at p= 0.05. Patient confidentiality and information governance were adhered to throughout this service evaluation and data analysis.",
//         "Ethical approval for this service evaluation waived by Epsom & St Helier University Hospitals NHS Trust. All data used in this service evaluation was retrospectively extracted. No patients, Next of Kins or GPs were contacted as part of this service evaluation All rights reserved. No reuse allowed without permission.",
