//         "Analysis of the admitted patients, by postcode, for their Index of Multiple Deprivation Decile and the average age of each decile subgroup demonstrated that the patients were predominantly from more affluent homes and that the average age of the patients rose with increasing affluence Figure 3 . All rights reserved. No reuse allowed without permission.",
