//         "The copyright holder for this preprint this version posted May 1, 2020. . By the morning of 14 th April 2020, 199 patients had been discharged to home or a care home, one patient had been discharged to a hospice (female 89, male 111). 163 patients had died (female 61, male 102). 131 remained in-patients at ESTH and 6 had been transferred to St George's or St Thomas' Hospitals; where they were still in-patients (female 66, male 71).",
